# Bruno API test collections. the request files (.bru), collection
# metadata (bruno.json) and READMEs are committed so the team can share
# API exercises. environments/* contains hardcoded mp/supabase dev
# secrets and any per-developer runtime values (e.g. userJwt written
# by the login request), so they stay local. regenerate credentials
# if they leak.
bruno/**/environments/
bruno/**/environments.bru

